    Note over Dev,OCP: Flow 1: Bundle Build (Konflux)

    Dev->>GH: Push commit / PR merge
    GH->>Konflux: Webhook trigger<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    Konflux->>GH: Clone repo<br/>HTTPS/443 GitHub Token
    Konflux->>Konflux: Build operator bundle image<br/>(operator-sdk bundle)
    Konflux->>QuayStg: Push bundle image<br/>HTTPS/443 Push Token
    Konflux->>Konflux: Build FBC catalog image<br/>(opm per OCP version)
    Konflux->>QuayStg: Push FBC image<br/>HTTPS/443 Push Token

    Note over Dev,OCP: Flow 1b: GitHub Actions Processing

    GH->>GHA: Trigger workflows
    GHA->>GHA: Bundle/FBC processing<br/>Nightly builds
    GHA->>QuayStg: Stage push<br/>HTTPS/443 Token

    Note over Dev,OCP: Flow 2: Release Validation

    Konflux->>EC: Submit for validation<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    EC->>EC: Enterprise contract checks
    EC-->>Konflux: Validation result

    Note over Dev,OCP: Flow 3: Operator Installation (OLM)

    OLM->>RegistryProd: Pull FBC catalog image<br/>HTTPS/443 Pull Secret
    OLM->>OLM: Parse catalog.yaml<br/>Resolve upgrade graph
    OLM->>RegistryProd: Pull bundle image<br/>HTTPS/443 Pull Secret
    OLM->>OCP: Create CSV, CRDs,<br/>RBAC, Deployment<br/>Kubernetes API TLS 1.2+
    OCP->>OCP: Deploy rhods-operator<br/>(3 replicas, 500m CPU)
    OCP->>OCP: Register webhooks<br/>(9443/TCP TLS)
    OCP->>OCP: Pull 92 RELATED_IMAGEs<br/>as needed

    Note over Dev,OCP: Flow 4: Runtime (Operator Active)

    OCP->>OCP: Webhook intercepts<br/>DSC/DSCI mutations<br/>9443/TCP TLS
    OCP->>OCP: Prometheus scrapes<br/>/metrics 8080/TCP<br/>Bearer Token
    OCP->>OCP: kubelet probes<br/>/healthz /readyz<br/>8081/TCP HTTP
